title: cyberdelinquents
extract:  Basically it is a criminal activity carried out by means of computers or the Internet.  The word delinquency is used with a reference to juvenile justice law. ...  Juvenile Cyber Delinquency is cyber crime committed by juveniles, which includes cyber theft, digital piracy, cyber bullying, cyber suicide, etc.Sep 17, 2015
